snippet.title: MiG-29 Fulcrum (Domark, 1991) gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for MiG-29 Fulcrum (Domark, 1991), Dos PC game produced by Domark in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/mig-29-fulcrum/6191/
MiG-29 Fulcrum (Domark, 1991) is an interesting game, a simulator fighters, war. There are six missions to take on, starting with your basic training.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
